7kaa
====
The music files cannot be distributed in the OpenBSD package due to
onerous licensing requirements. The game functions perfectly well
without music. However, should you want music, you can download the
files here:
https://www.7kfans.com/downloads/7kaa-music.tar.bz2

After untarring the file, copy the music/ directory to the 7kaa data
directory.

$ ftp https://www.7kfans.com/downloads/7kaa-music.tar.bz2
$ tar xjf 7kaa-music.tar.bz2
$ doas cp -R 7kaa-music/music ${TRUEPREFIX}/share/7kaa
